snippet.title: 13 WOOD ST - Horror Game (PC 2021)
snippet.description:
13 WOOD ST, a night in October: a long road, a dark forest and the house mentioned in the last will, making you the owner of a mysterious property. Welcome to 13 WOOD ST, a story rich horror game! Remastered 2022.


Download now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1727990/13_WOOD_ST


YouTube:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC5CPvhEWq_vSV-KDRD0hBhg

Website:
https://www.13woodst.com

Twitter:
https://twitter.com/13woodst


Music:
Bryan Teoh - Go On Without Me
